        <title>禾赛科技——全球领先的激光雷达研发与制造企业</title>
        <link>https://ai.programnotes.cn/p/%E7%A6%BE%E8%B5%9B%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A2%86%E5%85%88%E7%9A%84%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E9%9B%B7%E8%BE%BE%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%B6%E9%80%A0%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A/</link>
